owledge to the current understanding of functional brain networks in BPD. However, due to limitation of small sample sizes, the results of the current study should be viewed as exploratory and need to be validated on large samples in future works.},
author = {Xu, Tingting and Cullen, Kathryn R. and Mueller, Bryon and Schreiner, Mindy W. and Lim, Kelvin O. and Schulz, S. Charles and Parhi, Keshab K.},
